{"tid":876732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特首林鄭月娥同志稱呼習近平同志為「總書記」引起外界質關注其黨員身份","createTime":"2018-10-25T23:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-27T12:07:39.000Z","uid":155095,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e607c51cffff13c38bd96a6a7187e8128b456bac","tid":876732,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"https://www.post852.com/261961/【港珠澳通車】只有林鄭稱習近平「總書記」\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F261961%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E9%80%9A%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%91%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%89%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E7%A8%B1%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%8C%E7%B8%BD%E6%9B%B8%E8%A8%98%E3%80%8D&d=mmcIkk46CeecWPKyTqT64DOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=ea7079ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/261961/【港珠澳通車】只有林鄭稱習近平「總書記」</a>　游/<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/25192224/image1540466388533.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F25192224%2Fimage1540466388533.png&h=b490d825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋日前舉行開通儀式，特首林鄭月娥在致辭上稱呼習近平為「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">尊敬的習近平總書記</span></strong>」，而並非「國家主席」，與過往說法不同。<br />\n<br />\n游清源今日主持D100《龍鳳大茶樓》時表示，所有人都是叫主席，只有林鄭叫總書記，而總書記是黨的職務，無可能如此稱呼習近平，證明林鄭「出賣緊我哋啦」，已經「<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">入咗黨</span></strong>」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181024/s00022/4addf41cb6a6f61a8b6364a5e4456da6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181024%2Fs00022%2F4addf41cb6a6f61a8b6364a5e4456da6.jpg&h=caed3f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥同志與黨總書記習近平同志並排而行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/8/8d/港珠澳大橋.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F8d%2F%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B.jpg&h=7bf709cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/m4GkMpF1ipw/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fm4GkMpF1ipw%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d8a62a37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/14182550/image1521023039747.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F14182550%2Fimage1521023039747.png&h=28013a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首梁振英也是黨員同志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.iask.ca/uploads/allimg/120330/140TR142-0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iask.ca%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F120330%2F140TR142-0.jpg&h=9ac4ef0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73e0564495e4c322aa7cbb193a642c2cbbf3cbe0","tid":876732,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T23:54:39.000Z","msg":"選特首都係為左埋黨堆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60f5cced2700651a00d197d638edcc7c3ec2738","tid":876732,"uid":149973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da933925dad8635b05b2c537f1d518d3339c7d5c","tid":876732,"uid":56900,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"一定入黨架啦 有咩好報"},{"pid":"87c943ec0ada4aff2ae51ad6a28ccc56dd456f8e","tid":876732,"uid":140831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:20:45.000Z","msg":"你阿媽係女人"},{"pid":"204159b28c34a798e454396ff0263e6e2bebd8e6","tid":876732,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:28:21.000Z","msg":"咁